                <article> 

                    <h1 class="page-title">About Me</h1>

                    <div class="columns">

                        <div class="column is-two-thirds">

                            <div class="leading is-size-3-mobile is-size-3">
                                <p>Focused on designing and developing compelling digital products and experiences.</p>
                            </div>

                            <div>

                                <div class="bio">
                                    <p>My name is William Ukoh. I’m a Product Designer and Developer based in Lagos, Nigeria and I care about what I do. I have over 15 years experience designing and building web and mobile applications, platforms and services.</p>
                                    <p>I have always been passionate about the intersection of design, technology, and business. This has led me to work with individuals, companies and organizations in defining problems, putting in the work and achieving results.</p>
                                    <p>I enjoy speaking at events as well as teaching workshops on Product Design &amp; Management, UX and App Development. Currently, I am working as an Interactive Product Designer and Developer at GTBank.</p>
                                    <p>Outside of work, I love reading books, listening to music and podcasts, playing video games and watching football.</p>
                                    <p>Thanks for dropping by. You could have been anywhere in this virtual world, but you’re here. I appreciate it. Want to have a chat some day? Feel free to <a href="mailto:me@williamukoh.com">contact me</a>.</p>
                                </div>

